Footer:

- static Astro HTML
- no JS
- 3 to 4 useful columns
- clear internal links
- not oversized
- balanced spacing

Buttons:

- compact controls: 38px to 40px
- normal buttons: 44px
- large CTA: 46px to 48px
- no default shadow
- no scale animation
- consistent radius

Cards:

- compact padding on mobile
- comfortable padding on desktop
- consistent border/radius
- no random shadow
