## Typography

Use one sans-serif stack.

Do not load external Google Fonts at runtime.

Do not use decorative fonts.

Default scale:

- body: `text-base leading-7`
- nav/sidebar: `text-sm`
- labels: `text-sm font-medium`
- helper text: `text-xs leading-5`
- card titles: `text-base` or `text-lg font-semibold`
- section headings: `text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold`
- page H1: `text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight`
- modal title: `text-lg` to `text-xl font-semibold`

Avoid:

- `font-black`
- `font-extrabold`
- giant text in modals
- tiny muted text for important instructions
- inconsistent font weights between similar elements
- decorative uppercase everywhere

Important instructions must not rely on low-contrast muted text.

