## Color Usage

Primary action:

- blue/cyan

Premium / PRO:

- violet accent for selected premium states
- CTA may remain blue/cyan if it is the main action

Network/success:

- emerald/cyan indicator only

Danger:

- red

Warning:

- amber

Neutral UI:

- slate-like surfaces through semantic tokens

Do not use Solana neon green as the dominant UI color.

Do not use new colors unless:

- they map to an existing semantic meaning
- they are part of a protocol logo
- they are explicitly requested

