- check no React was added to header/sidebar/footer
- check no wallet/Reown/Solana import leaked into layout/static UI
- check light and dark mode
- check mobile width
- check desktop/tablet widths
- check no horizontal scroll
- check initial JS did not increase unnecessarily
- check `view-source` still contains meaningful HTML
- check package lock is not broken if dependencies changed

For wallet-related work, search build/source for:

```txt
@reown
@solana
wallet-adapter
web3.js
spl-token
```

These must not appear in the initial public layout bundle.

Allowed:

- static Reown imports only inside `src/lib/wallet/reown-client.ts`
- dynamic import after user action
- build chunks that are lazy-loaded only after wallet action

Not allowed:

- static imports in Header
- static imports in Sidebar
- static imports in Footer
- static imports in BaseLayout
- static imports in public static pages
